In this project, we have different stages of medallion architecture:
Stage 1 is ESS0 - Data come from other systems and stored in ESS0 tables. ESS0 has 3 tables:
	census_df - Metadata + json blob from dwelling form
	census_hsf - Metadata + json blob from household form
	census_if - Metadata + json blob from individual form

Stage 2 is ESS1 - Data is parsed from ESS0 and stored in ESS1 tables. ESS1 has 3 tables:
	dwelling - Social Census dwelling form parsed data
	household - Social Census household form parsed data
	individual - Social Census individual form parsed data

Stage 3 is ESS2 - The data from ESS1 is cleansed and technically validated, then fed into ESS2.

Similarly, there is ESS3 and ESS4.

Now, The first task is to move data from ESS0 to ESS1. For this task, there is parsing module developed by my teammate. I have integrated logging module in parsing process. 

